        <!-- OPENING PARAGRAPH-->
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-3">
            <div class="p-2 align-self-center">
                    <h1>What is Trinity Innovation Hub</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-3">
            <div class="p-2 align-self-center w-25">
                <p>The Innovation Hub provides a space for entrepreneurs, start-ups and innovation teams from large corporations. 
                    It will be the venue for organized regular events to bring together academics, start-ups, the local community and the enterprise community, animating and programming the Grand Canal Innovation District.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

